data.description: Room to grow. This property comes with a mother-in-law suite (casita). Mother-in-law suite has their own entrance, living room, kitchenette, full restroom and their own laundry. The main home has a great open concept living, dinning, and kitchen. It is open and great for entertainment. You will also find a half bathroom downstairs.   The gorgeous staircase leads up to a master suite with huge restroom and walk-in closet, 2 other bedrooms and a large laundry room.   The garage is a 3 car tandem garage. The backyard is has a great layout, perfect for a future pool.
